{
  "texts": [
    "Using deep-learning models (or algorithms), generative AI (Gen AI) creates new and novel output (e.g., text, image, video) from existing content.",
    "As such, Gen AI has substantially improved marketing outcomes across multiple domains.",
    "For example, leading companies use Gen AI to create suitable ad copy (Colburn, 2024): With Gen AI-created ad copy, Vanguard was able to increase conversion rates for its LinkedIn ads by 15%.",
    "Similarly, Emirates NBD bank (based in the UAE) relied on Gen AI to create personalized credit card offers that increased leads by 177%.",
    "Unilever also leveraged Gen AI in developing an application that crafts initial responses to customer messages by analyzing not only the issues that the customers raise, but also the sentiment underlying their messages."
  ]
}